Total long words: 16

Now plug these values into the LIX formula:
LIX = ((69/4) + (16/69)) * 100 
LIX = ((17.25) + (0.232)) * 100
LIX ≈ 17.482 

However we round to 1 dec place.
LIX ≈ 17.5
LIX = 17.5